aterra, su papá, Siward Woodward, tenía 24 años y su mamá, Helga de Chester, tenía 21 años. Se casó con Alice Wheaten el 14 de julio de 1077, en Yorkshire, Inglaterra. Fueron padres de por lo menos 1 hija. Murió el 29 de diciembre de 1104, en London, Middlesex, Inglaterra, a la edad de 61 años, y fue sepultado en London, Middlesex, Inglaterra."},"sv":{"14 May 1043–29 December 1104":"14 maj 1043–29 december 1104","1043–1104":"1043–1104","1056–1127":"1056–1127","1090–1165":"1090–1165","1020–1095":"1020–1095","1022–1094":"1022–1094","14 July 1077":"14 juli 1077","1090":"1090","29 December 1104":"29 december 1104","1066":"1066","1022":"1022","1165":"1165","1043":"1043","1086":"1086","1020":"1020","1096":"1096","1095":"1095","um 1090":"omkring 1090","1094":"1094","12 January 1105":"12 januari 1105","20 May 1043":"20 maj 1043","1127":"1127","1104":"1104","1056":"1056","14 May 1043":"14 maj 1043","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","London, Middlesex, England":"London, Middlesex, England","Lathom St James, Lancashire, England":"Lathom St James, Lancashire, England","Kent, England":"Kent, England"},"tl":{"14 May 1043–29 December 1104":"ika–14 ng Mayo 1043–ika–29 ng Disyembre 1104","1043–1104":"1043–1104","1056–1127":"1056–1127","1090–1165":"1090–1165","1020–1095":"1020–1095","1022–1094":"1022–1094","14 July 1077":"ika-14 ng Hulyo 1077","1090":"1090","29 December 1104":"ika-29 ng Disyembre 1104","1066":"1066","1022":"1022","1165":"1165","1043":"1043","1086":"1086","1020":"1020","1096":"1096","1095":"1095","um 1090":"mga 1090","1094":"1094","12 January 1105":"ika-12 ng Enero 1105","20 May 1043":"ika-20 ng Mayo 1043","1127":"1127","1104":"1104","1056":"1056","14 May 1043":"ika-14 ng Mayo 1043","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","London, Middlesex, England":"London, Middlesex, England","Lathom St James, Lancashire, England":"Lathom St James, Lancashire, England","Kent, England":"Kent, England"},"th":{"14 May 1043–29 December 1104":"14 พฤษภาคม 1043–29 ธันวาคม 1104",